Extended Ace editor:

This is actually ace editor ( http://ace.ajax.org/ ) in which we added toolbar with editor.
No need to manually write code for changing mode(syntax) , changing theme, changing font etc.
When ace editor is embeded in web page a toolbar come with editor,

Toolbar has buttons for open new File , fullscreen , change mode(syntax), change theme, change font, word wrpa toggle and help ,
We also add a functionality to toogle editor between textarea and editor.

See demo using Parikshak (An Automated Program Grading & Analysis Tool):
http://http://www.parikshak.in/ace_editor.html
http://http://www.parikshak.in/demo.html
